response.overview: This event took place on June 15th, 2024 at the KBS Hall in Kyoto, Japan. Matches featured • Bozilla vs. Komomo Minami • Marigold Superfly Title Tournament First Round Match: Misa Matsui vs. Myla Grace • Marigold Superfly Title Tournament First Round Match: Natsumi Showzuki vs. Zayda Steel • Nagisa Nozaki & Sareee vs. Mai Sakurai & Miku Aono • Kouki Amarei, MIRAI & Utami Hayashishita vs. Chika Goto, Nao Ishikawa & Victoria Yuzuki. The event was promoted by the Dream Star Fighting Marigold wrestling organization.
